<subSubSection pageId="689" pageNumber="690" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="689" pageNumber="690">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="689" pageNumber="690">This species ranges from southwestern Maine (Majka et al. 2011: 46) and southern Quebec (Larochelle 1975: 87) to western North Dakota, south to western (Dajoz 2007: 23) and northeastern Texas, southeastern Louisiana, and the Florida Panhandle (Peck and Thomas 1998: 21); also known from northern (Villa-Castillo and Wagner 2002: 246) and east-central Arizona [see Ball and Anderson 1962: Fig. 37].</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
